#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:45
msgid ""
"The three tenant-configured pages show or hide entirely based on whether the "
"tenant's `leftPanelSections` contains at least one section for that page. "
"Pages with no accessible sections for the current user are filtered out of "
"the top nav automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:47
msgid ""
"When tasks are pending, the page button for Projecten shows a count badge "
"(`tasks.length`) so caseworkers can see open work at a glance without "
"navigating there first."
