msgid ""
"The left panel is driven entirely by "
"`tenantConfig.leftPanelSections[activeTopNavPage]` — an array of section "
"objects configured per tenant in `public/tenants.json`. Switching the top-"
"nav page swaps the entire left-panel contents. Each section object has the "
"shape:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:65
