msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:69
msgid ""
"The `isPublic` flag controls whether the section is accessible without "
"authentication (see [Public and private sections]{1} below)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:71
msgid ""
"The active section is highlighted using the tenant's primary colour (`--"
"color-primary`). Clicking a section stores the choice in `sectionMemory` so "
"returning to the same top-nav page restores the last visited section rather "
"than defaulting to the first."
