msgid "Home tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:124
msgid ""
"The Home tab contains three public sections, all visible without "
"authentication."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:126
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api\\features\\caseworker-dashboard.md:126"
msgid "Nieuws"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:128
msgid ""
"Fetches the latest government news from the Rijksoverheid RSS feed via `GET /"
"v1/public/nieuws`. Items are shown as expandable cards with title, "
"publication date, and stripped body text. The feed is cached for 10 minutes "
"on the backend; on cache failure the stale result is returned to prevent a "
"blank UI."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:135
msgid "Berichten"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:137
msgid ""
"`BerichtenSection` is a self-contained component that fetches and renders "
"announcements from `GET /v1/public/berichten`. It owns its own fetch "
"lifecycle and requires no props beyond being mounted."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:139
msgid ""
"The data source changed in v2.9.3 from a hardcoded seed array to the live "
"Provincie Flevoland RSS feed. From the frontend perspective the contract is "
"unchanged — the component consumes the same `BerichtItem` shape it always "
"did."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:141
msgid ""
"Each card in the list shows the subject, preview, priority badge, and "
"publication date. When `item.action` is present, a **Lees meer →** anchor is "
"rendered in the card footer, linking directly to the source article on "
"flevoland.nl. This mirrors the pattern used by `NieuwsSection`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:143
msgid ""
"The section is registered as `{ id: \"berichten\", label: \"Berichten\", "
"isPublic: true }` in `leftPanelSections.home` for all tenants in "
"`tenants.json`, and appears above `nieuws`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:150
msgid "Producten & Diensten Catalogus"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:152
msgid ""
"`ProductenDienstenCatalogus` is a self-contained component that fetches "
"`GET /v1/public/producten-diensten` and renders the Provincie Flevoland "
"SC4.0 product feed as an expandable card grid. The section is only "
"configured in the Flevoland tenant's `leftPanelSections.home` in "
"`tenants.json`. It is publicly accessible — no login required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:154
msgid ""
"**Layout.** Products are displayed in a 2-column card grid, styled after "
"`RegelCatalogus`. Each card shows the product title and audience badges "
"(`Ondernemer`, `Particulier`). An **Online aanvragen** badge appears on "
"products where `onlineAanvragen` is `true`. Expanding a card reveals the "
"full description and a link to the product page on flevoland.nl."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:156
msgid ""
"**Filtering.** A free-text search field and an audience filter (Alle / "
"Ondernemer / Particulier) are rendered above the grid. Both filters operate "
"client-side on the full cached dataset."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:158
msgid ""
"**Stats row.** A summary row above the grid shows the total number of "
"visible products and the count of items with online aanvraag enabled."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:165
msgid ""
"To add this section to another tenant, add the following entry to that "
"tenant's `leftPanelSections.home` in `public/tenants.json`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:166
msgid ""
"{ \"id\": \"producten-diensten\", \"label\": \"Producten & Diensten\", "
"\"isPublic\": true }"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:170
msgid ""
"The backend service (`productenDiensten.service.ts`) currently hard-codes "
"the Flevoland SC4.0 feed URL. Serving a different feed for a different "
"tenant would require extending the service to accept a tenant parameter."
msgstr ""

