#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Ccaseworker-dashboard.md:212
msgid ""
"Each tenant defines its own left-panel section lists in `public/"
"tenants.json`. This means different organisation types (municipality, "
"province, national) can expose a different set of sections without any code "
"change:"
